Source: fwctl
Section: net
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Bernd Eckenfels <ecki@lina.inka.de>
Standards-Version: 2.5.1

Package: fwctl
Architecture: all
Depends: ${perl:Depends}, ipchains-perl, libnetwork-ipv4addr-perl, data-dumper, logrotate
Description: configure ipchains firewall using higher level abstraction
 This Perl Module and the script is used to generate ipchains rules from
 config files which are easy to use. It also handles accounting.
 .
 The rules will be installed from init and accounting data is dumped daily.
